{"tid":709451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（回馬槍） 普京訪中後  俄國禁止中國公司在貝加爾湖取水","createTime":"2018-06-20T04:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T10:27:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"833a85d140384fa3dcbd18b170684f02c907e2cd","tid":709451,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:19:32.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯總統普廷（Vladimir Putin）6月8日抵達北京，與中國國家主席習近平會晤，並展開為期3天的訪問行程，但就在普廷結束訪問中國後，俄羅斯法院14日就下令，禁止中國公司「貝加爾湖龍泉水廠」在湖邊生產瓶裝飲用水，出口中國。<br />\n<br />\n據美國之音（VOA）中文網報導，位在貝加爾湖畔的俄羅斯伊爾庫茨克州（Irkutsk）法院在14日裁決，禁止有中資背景的「貝加爾湖龍泉水廠」在湖邊生產瓶裝飲用水，以及出口到中國。俄羅斯法院對此裁決雖然沒提到是否因「政治因素」所造成，但有分析指出，這起裁決似乎顯示，俄羅斯對中國的威脅仍有所顧忌，所以才會特別警告中國別肖想貝加爾湖地區的相關資源。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，伊爾庫茨克洲法院則表示，是因為中國公司在生產瓶裝水的質量上違反相關規定，才遭到檢察官提出訴訟，要等到中國公司在生產質量上，符合當局健康衛生標準規範時，才會將禁令解除。<br />\n<br />\n伊爾庫茨克洲法院也提到，中國公司生產瓶裝水的水源是直接從貝加爾湖提取，但其大型工業設備在附近取水時，卻未控制水的品質。而其實當地低一級的法院早先曾對「貝加爾湖龍泉水廠」下達同樣的生產禁令，但「貝加爾湖龍泉水廠」不服提起上訴，伊爾庫茨克洲法院則裁決上訴無效，並維持原判。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2460093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2460093&d=GMefUb1EwwwOqWogq8hO0%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ff9835cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2460093&h=0ea8a775\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2460093</a><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45c7655874e2c813324bf50a8411d534036b2f2","tid":709451,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:27:07.000Z","msg":"要報復嗎？"},{"pid":"c3c17ed0290e449efb5b0d597554a00d14d8c74a","tid":709451,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1a24b5ee6949791aa05147380bcc579a325c5e","tid":709451,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i3.read01.com/SIG=360b5p2/304930525879325a564a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi3.read01.com%2FSIG%3D360b5p2%2F304930525879325a564a.jpg&h=c07344a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0191839cd2301480555c9f2a977ff72dae55de76","tid":709451,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"對老美就全力還拖<br />\n對老俄呢？咪又係鳩縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87aaadb5871076174a4a56efe2852345c77d74e4","tid":709451,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T10:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}